description: Triggers the backup job for the specified backup item. This is an asynchronous operation. To know the status of the operation, call GetProtectedItemOperationResult API.

vault_name.description: The name of the Recovery Services vault.

container_name.description: The container name associated with the backup item.

name.description: Resource name associated with the resource.

protected_item_name.description: The name of backup item used in this POST operation.

id.description: Resource ID represents the complete path to the resource.

fabric_name.description: The fabric name associated with the backup item.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group associated with the Recovery Services vault.

type.description: Resource type represents the complete path of the form Namespace/ResourceType/ResourceType/...
